para_trans: New Primary Health Centre sanctioned at Mauje Temni and Mauje Chulod T.G. Gondia
Government Decision No: Establishment-2024 / P.No.196 / Health-3
10th Floor, Gokuldas Tejpal Hospital Complex Building,
Read: Letter from Health Services Commissionerate, Mumbai No. A / C / Room-7A / T-5 / Precenter / Installation / Gondia / 2559-61/2024, D 01/07/2024.
Preamble: A proposal to sanction a new Primary Health Centre at Mauje Temni and Mauje Chulod T.G. Gondia was under consideration of the Government.
Government Decision- "Special for sanctioning new Primary Health Centre at Mauje Temni and Mauje Chulod T.G. Gondia"
As a matter of fact, this Government decision is being ratified. Prescribed for the above mentioned Primary Health Centre
Formal acquisition of land and creation of posts after completion of construction by the Zilla Parishad will be dealt with separately.
The decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra's www.maharashtra.gov.in website.
